# UI Feature Flags & Safe Launch

Gate risky UI features with flags; roll out with staged percentages and keep a kill switch available.

**Justification:** Reduces risk when iterating on customer-facing flows during campaigns.

## Progressive Delivery

```typescript
if (flags.enableNewDialer) { 
  return <NewDialer/> 
}
return <OldDialer/>
```

## Rollout Policy

- Start at internal 5–10%, expand to pilot users, then general availability
- Always include a kill switch in config

